name: Kulturligtvis
description: We created a website where people with an interest in culture and/or nature, can discover new places in Stockholm which are a bit unknown. We have listed a selection of different landmarks, and all registered users can connect with others who wants to visit the same location.

name: Twitter Clone
description: This is a Twitter inspired feed full of happy thoughts, built with React, HTML and CSS. I build and backend API, witch I fetched the thoughts from.

name: Netflix Clone
description: A React built website that shows the most popular movies in the US, where we fetched the data from an API

name: Spotify Clone
description: A website that shows the 50 most popular albums on Spotify right now. It's built with React, and we fetched an API from Spotify.

name: Tolkien Wishlist
description: An accessible website where you can make your own wishlist of Tolkien books, built with React.

name: To do list
description: A website with a to do list that counts how many tasks you have done, and how many's left. Built with React.

name: Halloween Quiz
description: A Halloween quiz with 8 questions, built in React and Redux.

name: Labyrinth Game
description: A labyrinth game built with React and Redux, using an API to handle the different game states.
